name: Sun Country Airlines Boeing 737-800 Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport
description:
Sun Country is an occasional visitor here in Calgary, operating casino charters to and from Bullhead City, Arizona. Here's one of their very colourful 737-800s arriving on 17L from IFP and departing an hour later for Seattle, with ATC included!

Thanks for watching!
